OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772125456
OL,3,CCould a tampon help detect early signs
OL,4,Cof cancer?
OL,6,FA new clinical trial is underway in
OL,7,FSouthampton which hopes a diagnostic
OL,8,Ftampon could improve how quickly
OL,9,Fovarian cancer is caught.
OL,11,FUniversity Hospital Southampton is
OL,12,Fleading the study where researchers
OL,13,Fwill see if the sanitary product can
OL,14,Fhelp compare vaginal fluid with cancer
OL,15,Fcells to help spot the early signs of
OL,16,Fthe disease.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
