FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772125456
OL,3,CCould a tampon help detect early signs
OL,4,Cof cancer?
OL,6,FCurrently there is no screening
OL,7,Fprocess for ovarian cancer and so
OL,8,Fdoctors must rely on patients to come
OL,9,Fforward with symptoms - such as
OL,10,Fpersistent bloating, stomach pain,
OL,11,Floss of appetite and feeling the need
OL,12,Fto urinate more often.
OL,14,FDr Jemma Longley, a Consultant Medical
OL,15,FOncologist said: "At the moment, the
OL,16,Ffocus of early detection is on blood
OL,17,Fbased markers. And that puts the onus
OL,18,Fon the participant or the patient to
OL,19,Fgo and find a health professional to
OL,20,Fdo that blood test.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772125456
OL,3,CCould a tampon help detect early signs
OL,4,Cof cancer?
OL,6,F"You have to be registered with the GP
OL,7,Fsurgery. You have to make time for
OL,8,Fthat. There's a lot of women that are
OL,9,Fvery busy these days with jobs and
OL,10,Fchildren and things.
OL,12,F"I wanted to figure out how we could
OL,13,Fmake a screening test that could be
OL,14,Fdone in your own home that was
OL,15,Fcommunity based and was accessible to
OL,16,Fall."
OL,18,FThe VIOLET study involves taking
OL,19,Fsamples of vaginal fluid from women
OL,20,Fwho are undergoing surgery for
OL,21,Fsuspected or confirmed ovarian cancer.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772125456
OL,3,CCould a tampon help detect early signs
OL,4,Cof cancer?
OL,6,FThe samples are then compared with
OL,7,Fthose from healthy volunteers. The
OL,8,Fteam will look for changes to
OL,9,Fbiomarkers called microRNAs, tiny
OL,10,Fbiological signals, that are present
OL,11,Fin both the ovarian cancer cells and
OL,12,Fthe vaginal fluid.
OL,14,FPatients consenting to being in the
OL,15,Ftrial will be given a diagnostic
OL,16,Ftampon pack. Inside that pack, they'll
OL,17,Fhave two tampons. They will be asked
OL,18,Fto insert the tampon between 20
OL,19,Fminutes and eight hours in the 24
OL,20,Fhours prior to their surgery.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772125456
OL,3,CCould a tampon help detect early signs
OL,4,Cof cancer?
OL,6,FOn the day of their surgery, they'll
OL,7,Fbring that back to the researchers.
OL,8,FWhen they have their surgery,
OL,9,Fresearchers will do a vaginal swap,
OL,10,Ftake a blood test and a urine test,
OL,11,Fand then get any tissue that is left
OL,12,Fover after the surgery.
OL,14,FDr Victoria Goss, Associate Professor
OL,15,Fof Early Diagnosis at the Southampton
OL,16,FClinical Trials Unit said: "Symptoms
OL,17,Fof ovarian ca
OL,19,Fncer can often crossover with other
OL,20,Fconditions.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772125456
OL,3,CCould a tampon help detect early signs
OL,4,Cof cancer?
OL,6,F"If we have these biomarkers of the
OL,7,Fearly stages of cancer, that means
OL,8,Fthat when patients are presenting
OL,9,Fpotentially with vague symptoms like a
OL,10,Fbit of abdominal pain, some weight
OL,11,Floss, then these biomarkers could be
OL,12,Fused to figure out whether or not that
OL,13,Fpatient actually does have cancer."
OL,15,FAccording to Cancer Research UK, on
OL,16,Faverage, 21 women a day are diagnosed
OL,17,Fwith ovarian cancer. However only
OL,18,Faround a quarter of cases are caught
OL,19,Fin the early stages.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772125456
OL,3,CCould a tampon help detect early signs
OL,4,Cof cancer?
OL,6,FIt is a study very much welcomed by Dr
OL,7,FAlison Farmer, a psycho-oncology nurse
OL,8,Fwho was diagnosed with ovarian cancer
OL,9,Fwhen she was 40. She underwent surgery
OL,10,Fto remove her ovaries, followed by
OL,11,Fchemotherapy.
OL,13,FAlison said: "I was very lucky enough
OL,14,Fto see a great team at the Princess
OL,15,FAnne Hospital and luckily, my ovarian
OL,16,Fcancer was caught early, which is
OL,17,Fquite unusual.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772125456
OL,3,CCould a tampon help detect early signs
OL,4,Cof cancer?
OL,6,F"There haven't been that many advances
OL,7,Fin ovarian cancer detection or
OL,8,Ftreatment over the years. And, you
OL,9,Fknow, sadly, a significant number of
OL,10,Fwomen are still dying despite some new
OL,11,Fdrugs.
OL,13,F"So I think anything like this, which
OL,14,Fis a reasonably easy study to do and
OL,15,Ftake part in, is really exciting."
OL,17,FIf the results of the study prove
OL,18,Fpromising, it could lead the way in
OL,19,Fdiagnosing other cancers.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772125456
OL,3,CCould a tampon help detect early signs
OL,4,Cof cancer?
OL,6,FDr Longley said: "This could be a
OL,7,Fmassive game changer for women
OL,8,Fdiagnosed with ovarian cancer and also
OL,9,Fother cancers of the gynaecological
OL,10,Ftract.
OL,12,F"We could open this up to different
OL,13,Fcancers - so cervical cancers and
OL,14,Fendometrial cancers and potentially
OL,15,Fcreate a multi-cancer early detection
OL,16,Ftest with a diagnostic tampon."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
