FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772125456
OL,3,CCould a tampon help detect early signs
OL,4,Cof cancer?
OL,6,FThe team is currently recruiting
OL,7,Fpatients at University Hospital
OL,8,FSouthampton but will look to recruit
OL,9,Fpatients from further afield during
OL,10,Fthe five-year study.
OL,12,FThe study is funded by a grant from
OL,13,FThe Eve Appeal with support from the
OL,14,FSouthampton Experimental Cancer
OL,15,FMedicine Centre and biotechnology
OL,16,Fcompany Daye.
OL,18,FAccording to NHS Choices, symptoms of
OL,19,Fovarian cancer include:
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
